spec_data.Name: python3-shortuuid
spec_data.Description:
A library that generates short, pretty, unambiguous unique IDs by using an
extensive, case-sensitive alphabet and omitting similar-looking letters and
numbers.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sat 29 Jul 2017 04:10:55 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: A generator library for concise, unambiguous and URL-safe UUIDs
